align=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: oops ...</span><hr size=1> You said you lost 2 clerics...How'd you lose 2 clerics?  Figuring out what killed them is probably your best bet to success.  Starting the CH cycle too early?  Having Druids/Shaman/Paladins/even Rangers all chain healing the MT for a few before the CH cycle even starts is a good way to make sure that the Clerics don't agro with their first CH.  Also, make sure your CH clerics aren't sitting down too early to med.  <br>
<br>
Clerics running out of mana can be rough.  Mod Rods and grouping them with a bard solely dedicated to manasongs is a very good start to this.  <br>
