<br>
How much of your force do you lose between your MT going down and then new MT taking over?  Once you learn to swtich effectively you should lose maybe 0-2 people between MTs.<br>
<br>
Druids and necros should be dotting the hell out of him.  If you have multiple of those classes spread the different DoTs between them to conserve mana and lower aggro.  Ro's firey sundering (dru) allows fire based spells to land for full most of the time.  Figure out how to stack damage shields, our mt on average has over 150pt damage shield on him.<br>
<br>
